{"id":4140,"date":"2024-12-16T13:40:30","date_gmt":"2024-12-16T13:40:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=4140"},"modified":"2024-12-16T13:40:30","modified_gmt":"2024-12-16T13:40:30","slug":"red-blue-orb","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/red-blue-orb\/","title":{"rendered":"Red Orb\/Blue Orb (Mega Stone)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Red Orb\/Blue Orb (Mega Stone)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Defeat Vega at the Battleground on Monday, Wednesday, or Friday, and then speak with him again a day later at the Crater Town Gym.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Mega Evolution<\/th>\n<td>Groudon\/Kyogre<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Beat the Elite Four to unlock the Battleground<\/li>\n<li>Ensure the day is Monday, Wednesday, or Friday<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Seaport City Pokemon Center before following the path south.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/01-pokemon-unbound-walking-south-from-the-seaport-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Walking south from the Seaport City Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking south from the Seaport City Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the first turn down and enter the first house you see on your left.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-seaport-city-battleground.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the Seaport City Battleground. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the Seaport City Battleground.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Vega appears here at the Battleground on Mondays, Wednesdays, and Fridays.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/03-pokemon-unbound-approaching-vega-inside-the-battleground.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching Vega inside the Battleground. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching Vega inside the Battleground.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Speak with Vega and challenge him individually to a battle (not a gauntlet). Below is his team composition:<\/p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\">\n<table class=\"table grey left aligntop\" style=\"min-width:800px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"6\" class=\"text-large center\">Gym Leader Vega<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/04-pokemon-unbound-gym-leader-vega.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/sprites\/pokemon\/weavile.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/sprites\/pokemon\/hydreigon.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/sprites\/pokemon\/spiritomb.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/sprites\/pokemon\/greninja.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/sprites\/pokemon\/absol-mega.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Pok\u00e9mon<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>Weavile (Level 82)<\/td>\n<td>Hydreigon (Level 84)<\/td>\n<td>Spiritomb (Level 83)<\/td>\n<td>Greninja (Level 83)<\/td>\n<td>Mega Absol (Level 84)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Type<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>Dark\/Ice<\/td>\n<td>Dark\/Dragon<\/td>\n<td>Ghost\/Dark<\/td>\n<td>Water\/Dark<\/td>\n<td>Dark\/Fairy<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Ability<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>Pickpocket<\/td>\n<td>Levitate<\/td>\n<td>Pressure<\/td>\n<td>Battle Bond<\/td>\n<td>Pressure &#8211; Magic Bounce<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Held Item<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>Focus Sash<\/td>\n<td>Life Orb<\/td>\n<td>Leftovers<\/td>\n<td>Darkinium Z<\/td>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/absolite\/\">Absolite<\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Weaknesses<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Fighting (4x)<\/li>\n<li>Rock (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Bug (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Steel (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fire (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Fighting (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Bug (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Ice (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Dragon (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (4x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Fighting (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Bug (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Grass (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Electric (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Poison (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Steel (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Moves<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Knock Off<\/li>\n<li>Triple Axel<\/li>\n<li>Ice Shard<\/li>\n<li>Poison Jab<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Dark Pulse<\/li>\n<li>Earth Power<\/li>\n<li>Flamethrower<\/li>\n<li>Nasty Plot<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Snarl<\/li>\n<li>Calm Mind<\/li>\n<li>Will-O-Wisp<\/li>\n<li>Protect<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Water Shuriken<\/li>\n<li>Surf<\/li>\n<li>Dark Pulse<\/li>\n<li>Ice Beam<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Knock Off<\/li>\n<li>Close Combat<\/li>\n<li>Play Rough<\/li>\n<li>Swords Dance<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<p>Defeating Vega will reward you with the Darkinium Z.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/05-pokemon-unbound-acquiring-the-darkinium-z.jpg\" alt=\"Acquiring the Darkinium Z. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Acquiring the Darkinium Z.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>With Vega defeated, wait for the next day. Then fly to Crater Town and walk toward the town\u2019s center.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/06-pokemon-unbound-walking-toward-crater-towns-center.jpg\" alt=\"Walking toward Crater Town\u2019s center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking toward Crater Town\u2019s center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then enter the Crater Town Gym.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/07-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-crater-town-gym.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the Crater Town Gym. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the Crater Town Gym.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Navigate the gym and reach Vega to speak with him. <\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/08-pokemon-unbound-approaching-vega.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching Vega. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching Vega.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Here, Vega will give you the Red and Blue Orbs.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/09-pokemon-unbound-acquiring-the-red-orb-from-vega.jpg\" alt=\"Acquiring the Red Orb from Vega. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Acquiring the Red Orb from Vega.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__